  <p>Block 4 covers coastal processes — longshore drift, wave erosion, beach accretion, coastal landforms — and the role of monsoon storms. Two contrasting coastal stories: <strong>Marina Beach</strong> (one of the world's longest urban beaches, monsoon-driven sediment cycling) and the <strong>Mahabalipuram coast</strong> (rock-cut temples on 1300-Mya granite, 1000+ years of human modification + ongoing coastal processes). Student work: pick a coastal Chennai location and identify 2 current coastal processes shaping it.</p>
